   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="header">
            <p>Geschäft der Anna, Gattin des Ulrich Dyetram</p>
         </div>
         <div type="entry" resp="rs-cs">
            <p> pr. mü., Einbr. 2 Zg., Ma (Inde~: Item gescheft Annen Ulreichs Dietram uxor) <rs
                  type="event" ref="#ev__StB_I_4">Des nachsten phincztags nach sand Andres tag kom
                  auch fur den rat <rs type="fn" role="witness"><rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__ulrich_dietram_StB_I_4">Ulreich der Dyetram</rs> und hat da beweist
                     mit den erbern priestern zu rechter zeit, als er ze recht solt, mit <rs
                        type="person" ref="#pe__jakob_StB_I_4"><roleName type="title"
                              ><add>erbern</add></roleName>
                        <roleName type="prof"><add>priester</add></roleName>
                        <roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Jacoben <roleName type="occ" corresp="#org__wien-st_stephan"><add>curherren</add></roleName></rs> und
                        <rs type="person" ref="#pe__stephan_StB_I_4"><roleName type="title"
                              ><add>erbern</add></roleName>
                        <roleName type="prof"><add>priester</add></roleName>
                        <roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Stephann, die zeit bayd <roleName type="occ" corresp="#org__wien-st_stephan">curherren</roleName> dacz
                        Sand Stephan ze Wienn</rs></rs>, das geschefft, so <rs type="fn"
                     role="issuer"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__anna_StB_I_4">sein <roleName
                           type="kin" corresp="#pe__ulrich_dietram_StB_I_4">hawsfraw</roleName> Anna,
                           <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__wolfhard_pob_QGW_II_I_1011"
                              ><add>tochter</add></roleName>
                        <rs type="person" ref="#pe__wolfhard_pob_QGW_II_I_1011">Wolfharts tochter des
                           Poben</rs></rs></rs>, getan hat. Also das si geschaft hat dem vorgenanten
                     <rs type="fn" role="recipient"><rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__ulrich_dietram_StB_I_4">irm <roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__anna_StB_I_4">wirt</roleName> Ulreichen dem Dyetramen</rs>
                     <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_I">die drey <rs type="place"
                           ref="#pl__sievering-immo_12">weingerten <roleName type="topo"
                              corresp="#pl__sievering">ze Sufring</roleName> ledichleich, ayner
                           genant die Junkchfraw</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="#pl__sievering-immo_13"
                              ><roleName type="topo" corresp="#pl__sievering"><add>ze
                              Sufring</add></roleName>der ander der Chunringer</rs> und <rs
                           type="place" ref="#pl__sievering-immo_14"><roleName type="topo"
                              corresp="#pl__sievering"><add>ze Sufring</add></roleName>der drit der
                           Jüdel</rs>, <triggerstring n="impl_rules">in solicher weise, <rs
                              type="event" ref="#ev__StB_I_4_men_1">als <rs type="fn"
                                 role="recipient"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__anna_StB_I_4"
                                 >ir</rs></rs>
                              <rs type="fn" role="transactiongood_I"><rs type="place"
                                    ref="#pl__sievering-immo_12">die</rs><rs type="place"
                                    ref="#pl__sievering-immo_13"><add>die</add></rs><rs type="place"
                                    ref="#pl__sievering-immo_14"><add>die</add></rs></rs>
                              <rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs type="person"
                                    ref="#pe__friedrich_dietram_QGW_II_I_1026">Fridreich der Dyetram,
                                    des egenanten Ulreichs <roleName type="kin"
                                       corresp="#pe__ulrich_dietram_StB_I_4"
                                 >vetter</roleName></rs></rs>, <triggerstring n="disp">gegeben
                                 hat</triggerstring></rs></triggerstring>.</rs></rs> Als darumb die
                  obgenanten her Jacob und her Stephan bey irer priesterschaft und gewizzen und der
                  vorgenant <rs type="fn" role="other"><rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__friedrich_dietram_QGW_II_I_1026">Fridreich der Dyetram <roleName
                           type="rep" corresp="#pe__anna_StB_I_4"><add>beweist</add></roleName></rs>
                     <triggerstring n="fn"><add>beweist</add></triggerstring></rs> mit seinen trewn an
                  ayde stat vor offem rat habent gesagt, als si ze recht solten.</rs>
            </p>
         </div>
